metadata.name: Stratton Copemont - Aunt Emma - 10 of Hearts
metadata.description: Introducing the Stratton Copemont Royal Flush NFTs - a collection of 5 sets, each consisting of 200 NFTs. These exclusive NFTs will be airdropped to our community, with additional rewards for holders post presale launch, including an airdrop of $STRAT Tokens. Collect all 5 characters for a chance to win a substantial reward!
